The paper discusses the use of cooperative communication and machine learning algorithms for relay selection in power line communication networks. This topic falls under the intersection of several computer science sub-disciplines, including information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.IT and cs.NI, followed by cs.LG, cs.SY, and cs.AI.
